{
  "stem": "26609.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they marched them-- they had to walk to their deaths.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had to walk through the city, right-- there was a road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Eh, that road was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Olitza ?] Lwowska.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's where the gymnasium was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I told you where I attended it in Lwowska.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And a long road-- and that road led to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That's why the name, Lwowska, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Olitza ?] Lwowska.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a long way they marched them, they had to walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think that my parents or other people-- there was still young people there, because my mother was only in her 50s, early 50s.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they marched them to a place before Lwow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how many kilometers it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't think that many people reached that place where they killed them all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a-- [NON-ENGLISH] How do you say a [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Forest.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Forest?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A forest?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it wasn't exactly a forest, something like it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not a garden, but that was a place between garden and forest-- something like it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, they shot them all, killed them all, one by one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But how many people came there alive, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they-- they were undernourished-- not food in the last year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even my mother said, when she-- how I knew about my brother-- that was-- before they killed them, they let them stay in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother, somewhere-- I don't know where she got some money, but-- I don't know if my mother was one of them, or-- there were probably more mothers like my mother.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
